thread.title: Janie Emerson
thread.title_full: Totally Wicked E-liquid USA inc. reviewed by Janie Emerson

author: Janie Emerson
title: Janie Emerson
text: I am very happy with my purchases. They were on sale and I am thrilled to be able to stock up before the Tobacco Companies stop the sale of ecigs. I am so sad that they would be so evil. I was addicted to cigarettes for 35 yrs and they were harmful to me but I couldn't quit. I started using vaping in 2009 and never picked up a cigarette again. I don't vape all the time now but I like to have them around so I never have the urge to smoke again.
